manifest.name: @sentry-internal/tracing
manifest.readme: ## Sentry Internal Tracing Package - Do not use directly, for internal use only This is an internal package that is being used to migrate @sentry/tracing code to its respective runtime packages. For v8, @sentry/tracing will be dropped and the code in this package will be split into @sentry/browser and @sentry/node.
